thodari ( english : the train ) is a 2016 indian tamil-language film co produced , written and directed by prabhu solomon .   the film produced by sathya jyothi films stars dhanush and keerthy suresh in the lead roles , while d. imman composes the film 's music .   along with a telugu dubbed version rail , the film was released in theatres on 22 september 2016 .